      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃーーん！　渚ちゃーーん！！\n一緒にお昼食べよーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chanーー! Nagisa-chanーー!!\nLet's have lunch togetherーー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4823353131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "め、芽衣、声が大きいってば。みんな見てるから……\nとりあえず、中庭に行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-Mei‚ your voice is too loud. Everyone is watching…\nFirst‚ let's go to the courtyard",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4823353131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1999999046
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.1109070778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "今日、渚ちゃんお休みなんだ～？\n何かお仕事入ってたっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ is Nagisa's day off~?\nDoes she have work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1609070778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0603631179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "バラエティ番組に出るって言ってた\n『本好きが選ぶおすすめの書店巡り』、だったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said she was going on a variety show\nWas it‚ \"Bookstore Tour Recommended by a Bookworm\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0603631179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.5404314201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "面白そう！　いつ放送かなぁ？\n楽しみだね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds interesting! When will it air?\nLooking forward to it~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5404314201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9119054318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "さてと、それじゃあ……\nわああああああああああ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ then…\nWaaaaaaaaaa!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9619054318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8999999046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "お弁当、寮に忘れちゃった……！！\nどうしよう、お昼抜きになっちゃうよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lunch box‚ I left it at dorm…!!\nWhat should I do‚ my lunch is goneー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7750561874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4290687721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで手ぶらなんだろう、とは思ったけど……\nしょうがないわね。私の、半分食べる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wondered‚ why you were empty-handed…\nIt's what it is. Would you like to have half of mine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4290687721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3058487734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "いいの！？　ごめんね、ありがとう……\nからあげ、一個もらってもいい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that okay!? Sorry‚ thank you…\nFried chicken‚ can I have one…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3058487734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.5926514467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5926514467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.1167748809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがと～！　じゃあ、あ～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you~! Then‚ ah~hh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1167748809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4212873658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "口開けてないで、自分で取って\nほら、つまようじあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't open your mouth‚ take it yourself\nHere‚ I have some toothpicks",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4212873658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.3418314021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あむ……ん～、心に染みるよぉ……\nでも、どうすればお弁当を忘れなくなるんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yum… umm~‚ I'm into it…\nBut‚ how can I stop forgetting my lunch box…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3418314021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2389290851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "何か工夫出来るならいいんだろうけど、基本的には\n忘れないように、気をつけるしかないんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be nice if we could come up with some ideas‚ basically‚\nyou have to be careful not to forget‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2389290851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1921260239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "工夫……。逆に、絶対に忘れないものってなんだろう\nスマホとか……。あ、分かった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ideas…. On the other hand‚ what is something I never forget?\nA Smartphone or…. Ah‚ I got it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1921260239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.431307034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "スマホにお弁当箱をくっつけておけばいいんだよ！\nキーホルダーみたいに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just display something related to lunchbox on my smartphone!\nLike a key holder!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.431307034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.1952728949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "そうすれば、ないないー！　ってなった時も\n電話かければすぐに見つかるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I do that‚ even if there comes a time when No-No—!‚\nI'll be able to tell right away when I use the phone‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1952728949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.2360440615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとイメージ出来ないんだけど……\n工夫しようっていう努力は偉いと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something doesn't come to mind clearly…\nI think the effort to solve it is great",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2360440615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.1344061259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、やったー！\n……ねぇ琴乃ちゃん、卵焼きも、もらっていい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ that's it!\n…Hey‚ Kotono-chan‚ can I have some egg rolls‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1344061259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.8806871139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mei_01_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8806871139,
